# Output artefacts from the research / live-scan CLI tools.
# ac_probe.py writes {timestamp}_probe.json, ac_monitor.py writes
# {timestamp}_out.json; both default to cwd, so users running from
# the repo root will leak these files. Belt-and-braces ignore so a
# stray run never gets committed.
*_probe.json
*_out.json
